name: La Blasphemia
description:
Your matter matters not, so sin without limit, and find your way to us..

All creepy words aside, this is actually a latex "pull" of a prosthetic makeup I created back in 2009. I colored it with alcohol-soluble paints and liquid vinyl for a dry "wet" look on the tongue and other spots. For fun, I put the mask over a marble copy of virgin Mary's face in "Pieta".
